description:
## Latest Update
In latest version of dataset I updated Gender, Winner, Total Assets and Liabilities.

## Context
Data set for people who love Politics and Data Science.
Checkout web scrapping code in my github repo:
https://github.com/themlphdstudent/kaggle/tree/master/datasets

## Acknowledgements
The data has been crawled from the https://myneta.info/ website.
Photo by [Parker Johnson](https://unsplash.com/@pkripperprivate?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText) on [Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/s/photos/voting?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText).

## Inspiration
This dataset is scrapped especially for beginners of data science and some one who wants to know more about Indian politicians.

Which state has highest number of candidates with criminal cases?
Candidate with highest education.
Candidates with lowest education.
Other Ideas.
title: Lok Sabha Election Candidate list (2004 to 2019)
